00:48:17,064 --> 00:48:18,232
Vrata.

454
00:48:26,991 --> 00:48:29,160
Gde su mi majka i sestra?

455
00:48:40,963 --> 00:48:42,089
Gde su?

456
00:48:45,259 --> 00:48:47,428
Ovde, medju ovim zidovima.

457
00:48:48,679 --> 00:48:51,265
Guverner se oporavlja.
Ostace zive.

458
00:48:53,476 --> 00:48:55,436
Naravno, bice kaznjene.

459
00:48:59,190 --> 00:49:00,983
Da li je moguce?

460
00:49:04,195 --> 00:49:07,365
Da li je moguce
da mozes ovo da uradis?

461
00:49:07,531 --> 00:49:10,451
Ljudi koje znas?
Porodica koju si voleo?

462
00:49:12,662 --> 00:49:15,873
Pustices ih.
Rado ces ih pustiti, Messala?

463
00:49:20,294 --> 00:49:23,381
Nisam pokusao da ubijem guvernera!
Ja nisam ubica!

464
00:49:23,631 --> 00:49:25,299
Znam da nisi.

465
00:49:26,717 --> 00:49:28,511
Znas?

466
00:49:32,556 --> 00:49:33,724
Ti si zao!

467
00:49:34,225 --> 00:49:36,644
Ne, Judah, ja nisam zao.

468
00:49:37,395 --> 00:49:39,146
Zeleo sam tvoju pomoc.

469
00:49:39,897 --> 00:49:41,857
Sada si mi je dao.

470
00:49:42,566 --> 00:49:45,903
Dajuci tvoj primer
obeshrabrio sam izdajnike.

471
00:49:46,237 --> 00:49:50,199
Osudjujuci bez oklevanja
starog prijatelja, postacu strah.

472
00:49:52,827 --> 00:49:54,912
Ali ne moju porodicu.

473
00:49:56,330 --> 00:49:57,999
Pusti ih.

474
00:49:58,749 --> 00:49:59,667
Molim te.

475
00:50:02,169 --> 00:50:04,588
-Mesala, preklinjem te.
Preklinjes!?

476
00:50:07,842 --> 00:50:09,927
Zar ja tebe nisam preklinjao?

477
00:50:15,224 --> 00:50:18,019
Ti si izabrao ovo.
Nema se vise sta reci.

478
00:50:18,853 --> 00:50:21,188
Ubij me, i tvoja majka i sestra
ce umreti...

479
00:50:21,355 --> 00:50:23,774
...razapete na krstu pred tobom.

480
00:50:25,776 --> 00:50:27,445
Hajde, Judah.

481
00:50:28,571 --> 00:50:29,822
Ubij me.

482
00:50:42,752 --> 00:50:45,046
Neka mi Bog pruzi osvetu.

483
00:50:45,254 --> 00:50:49,133
Molicu se da pozivis
dok se ja vratim.

484
00:50:50,134 --> 00:50:51,218
Vratis?

485
00:50:56,640 --> 00:50:57,892
Drzite ga.

486
00:51:34,470 --> 00:51:35,846
Straza, pozdrav.

487
00:51:38,015 --> 00:51:39,767
Tribun ce vas primiti sada.

488
00:52:11,298 --> 00:52:14,802
Tribune, ja sam upravnik
kuce Hura.

489
00:52:16,178 --> 00:52:17,638
Secam te se.

490
00:52:17,847 --> 00:52:21,726
Bili smo na putu za Antiohu
kad smo cui sta se dogodilo.

491
00:52:21,892 --> 00:52:25,771
Judah Ben-Hur nije mogao to uciniti.
Poznavali ste ga, tribune.

492
00:52:25,980 --> 00:52:27,565
Bolje od tebe.

493
00:52:27,732 --> 00:52:32,236
Onda se ne smete premisljati,
optuzbe su neosnovane.

494
00:52:32,570 --> 00:52:34,655
Zatvorenicima su odredjene kazne.

495
00:52:35,072 --> 00:52:37,158
Osudjeni su?
