508
00:55:25,409 --> 00:55:26,494
Evo.

509
00:55:49,433 --> 00:55:50,559
Cekaj.

510
00:55:51,602 --> 00:55:53,270
Za njega nema vode.

511
00:56:15,292 --> 00:56:16,711
Gospode...

512
00:56:17,461 --> 00:56:19,463
