00:58:10,574 --> 00:58:12,076
Ustaj!

518
00:58:12,368 --> 00:58:13,828
Neka krenu!

519
00:58:16,956 --> 00:58:20,418
Ti, nazad na svoje
mesto!

520
00:58:23,421 --> 00:58:25,423
Napred, psi.

521
00:59:30,655 --> 00:59:33,157
Uskoro ce konzulov camac
pristati uz brod.

522
00:59:33,407 --> 00:59:35,242
Budite spremni da podignete vesla.

523
00:59:41,499 --> 00:59:44,335
Dizi vesla!

524
00:59:46,837 --> 00:59:48,923
Dole vesla!

525
01:00:07,358 --> 01:00:09,151
Novi komandant, Quintus Arrius.

526
01:00:30,297 --> 01:00:32,383
Koliko veslaca?
200, konzule.

527
