01:13:27,325 --> 01:13:28,367
Pali.

620
01:13:41,088 --> 01:13:42,173
Pali!

621
01:13:42,757 --> 01:13:43,841
Pali!

622
01:13:49,555 --> 01:13:51,515
Spremi se za podizanj vesla.

623
01:13:53,017 --> 01:13:55,811
Dizi vesla. Dizi!

624
01:13:56,103 --> 01:13:58,022
Povlacenje.

625
01:14:00,608 --> 01:14:01,651
Udesno!

626
01:14:09,492 --> 01:14:11,118
Izbaci vesla!

627
01:14:12,787 --> 01:14:14,038
Pali!

628
01:14:35,559 --> 01:14:37,186
Pazi!
Pali!

629
01:14:53,786 --> 01:14:56,831
U proboj! Naredi dole!

630
01:14:56,998 --> 01:14:58,374
Probijanje!

631
01:15:10,678 --> 01:15:13,180
Conzule, galija ide ka nama.

632
01:15:20,771 --> 01:15:24,442
Udaricemo!
Udaricemo!

633
01:20:19,528 --> 01:20:20,905
Zasto si me spasao?

634
01:20:23,824 --> 01:20:26,327
Zasto ste mi skinuli lance?

635
01:20:46,931 --> 01:20:49,558
Kako se zoves, 41?

636
01:20:51,769 --> 01:20:53,312
Judah Ben-Hur.

637
01:20:54,355 --> 01:20:56,232
Judah Ben-Hur...

638
01:20:57,900 --> 01:20:59,276
...pusti me da umrem.

639
01:21:02,488 --> 01:21:05,700
Cuvamo vas da sluzite ovom brodu.

640
01:21:06,242 --> 01:21:07,702
Veslajte dobro i zivite.

641
